{"tid":1026684,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"8個月空白期定寫半年經驗好","createTime":"2019-02-18T09:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T15:06:20.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cceaef83d741a8df3bd284e84c064cd553509bd3","tid":1026684,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一份工前年6月返，做一年到上年6月resign轉新工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二份上年7月頭返，人工多20%，不過太難頂冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三份就而家嗰份，上年8月中返，人工比第一份多30%，可能工種少少唔同所以耐少少先上手，去到11月頭話我表現唔夠好，一次過extend我3個月試用期，計我話公司諗縮數，年尾雙糧花紅唔想出俾我就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最弊年尾難搵工，點都捱埋過年先，上星期二半年試用期去到最後一日，趁7日通知期即刻遞信，到今日last day，頭先原本滿心歡喜地去hr拎工作證明，點知工作證明寫住話未過試用期resign，同hr拗數，我話唔想張證明寫住未過試用期，點知hr話規定係咁，冇得改，心情即刻：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> --&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> --&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> --&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> --&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街，就係寫多三隻字&quot;in probation period&quot;，搞到我份工作證明變廢紙，本身仲有幾個字就可以脫苦海，而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早知遲一日先遞信，雖然捱多一個月，點都起碼有得寫落cv，而家咁樣唔寫落cv，過埋今個月真係8個月空白期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598793d0d97265ae3132e0a87d164b13b3a446de","tid":1026684,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d0b406ad5b68cfa2b59d842a4635dffc63bf9b","tid":1026684,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"首先點解你覺得resign in probation period係廢紙"},{"pid":"7feb186e46388b8e17fde08c4cbf39f3513e473d","tid":1026684,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"b1d0b406ad5b68cfa2b59d842a4635dffc63bf9b","tid":1026684,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"首先點解你覺得resign in probation period係廢紙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"人地hr會先入為主，覺得係咪工作態度有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年8月到今年2月成半年都未過試用期，hr睇到都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f83cd38171f5a9b619849982c57caee2f52e989","tid":1026684,"uid":10038,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:04:32.000Z","msg":"其實人地extend你三個月應該係想你辭職"},{"pid":"417e5fa1eaefb7b03c397a8ba4b5eb05ae6adcce","tid":1026684,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7feb186e46388b8e17fde08c4cbf39f3513e473d","tid":1026684,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"b1d0b406ad5b68cfa2b59d842a4635dffc63bf9b","tid":1026684,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"首先點解你覺得resign in probation period係廢紙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"人地hr會先入為主，覺得係咪工作態度有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年8月到今年2月成半年都未過試用期，hr睇到都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"多如啦 一做reference check就知"},{"pid":"728b6b7e4540da2e98495fdfc8636596a7095212","tid":1026684,"uid":54415,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"搵份有手有腳就請既工洗洗底，惡哽都要hea年幾先再搵"},{"pid":"9769851b47d50119e